    • isInput

      public boolean isInput
      Indicates whether the impact direction of the flow of this factor is `input` or `output`; e.g. for an emission the direction is `output` while for a resource it is `input`. If it is `input`, the matrix value is set to a negative value (as in the corresponding intervention matrix).
